data.description:
Great family home located in Legacy Subdivision.  Open floor plan features a gas fireplace in the living room, granite countertops throughout, under cabinet lighting, and breakfast bar.  4BR/3BA with remote master featuring separate shower and whirlpool tub, and his and hers walk-in closets. 4th bedroom located upstairs could also be used as a family/game/exercise area.  It features a walk-in closet as well as a full bathroom.  Storage space added  under stairs could also be used as a hangout for pets.  Newly built cedar craftsman style fence provides privacy without completely obstructing the view.  2 car garage. Motivated Sellers!  

Master Bedroom - 14'10" x 15'10"
Second Bedroom - 10'10" x 12'8"
Third Bedroom - 11'5" x 10'10"
Fourth Bedroom - 16'7" x 20'9"


Legacy subdivision amenities include swimming pool, fishing ponds, playground, baseball area, and lots of common grounds for various outdoor activities.  Events are held throughout the year such as food truck nights, Easter egg hunts, and cookies with Santa.

Highly sought after Bossier schools to include Legacy Elementary (walking distance), Benton Middle, and Benton High.

**Up to 3% commission offered to buyer's agent
**Buyer pre-qualification required prior to showing

If you need help with pre-qualifying contact Stephanie Smith with Union Home Mortgage @ 318-302-6707 or email ssmith@unionhomemortgage.com.
